723298f-a.title: Manhattan: South Street - Dover Street
723298f-a.text:
South Street, under the Brooklyn Bridge, showing several
warehouses that face the East River, and from which the photo-
Erapher is viewing. These bear No's. 168-70 South Street. They
are between Dover and Foosevelt Street's.
Ootober 1927
George L. Balgue, photo
MAY BE REPRODUCED

719332f-a.title: Manhattan: Dover Street - South Street
719332f-a.text:
Dover Street, north side, west from South Street. This view
also shows South Street, west side, at Dover Street.
May 3, 1932.
PC L2 Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
